---
/**
 * EmptyState — fresh-clone onboarding card.
 *
 * Shown on `/` when data/briefings/ has zero files. Uses the same type scale
 * as briefing cards; no box, no card — just typographic rhythm.
 */
---

<section class="empty-state" aria-labelledby="empty-title">
  <h2 id="empty-title">아직 브리핑이 없어요</h2>
  <p>
    이 저장소를 방금 clone 했다면<br />
    아래 7단계로 첫 브리핑을 생성하세요.
  </p>

  <ol>
    <li><code>.env</code> 에 <code>GEMINI_API_KEY</code> 설정</li>
    <li><code>yt-dlp</code> 설치 (<code>brew install yt-dlp</code>)</li>
    <li><code>config.yaml</code> 에 유튜브 채널과 블로그 소스 추가</li>
    <li><code>scripts/resolve-channel-ids.py</code> 로 UC... ID 조회</li>
    <li>NotebookLM 로그인 (선택)</li>
    <li><code>python pipeline/run.py</code></li>
    <li><code>npm run dev</code></li>
  </ol>

  <a href="https://github.com" class="cta">README 보기 →</a>
</section>
